{Speech 2 Answer 11}{}{No little gems today.}
{Speech 2 Answer 5}{}{Who're you?}
{Speech 2 Answer Exit}{}{Bye.}
{Speech 3}{}{Время:60000 Нет ответа:Завершить диалог}
{Speech 3 Answer Exit}{}{No, none turned up today. Well, if I see any -- I'll let you know.}
{Speech 3 Answer 6}{}{What's your name?}
{Speech 3 Answer Exit*}{}{No, nothing.}
{Speech 4}{}{Время:60000 Нет ответа:Завершить диалог}
{Speech 4 Answer Exit}{}{No, none turned up today. Well, if I see any -- I'll let you know.}
{Speech 4 Answer 5}{}{What's your name?}
{Speech 4 Answer Exit*}{}{No, nothing.}
{Speech 4 Answer 18}{}{I just can't find that acquaintance of yours. Where did you say you met him?}
{Speech 4 Answer 19}{}{Oh no, I've had quite enough of that stash of yours...}
{Speech 5}{}{Me? I'm Mickey, the polite and considerate treasure hunter from Broken Hills.}
{Speech 5 Answer 7}{}{A hunner?}
{Speech 5 Answer Exit}{}{Bye-bye.}
{Speech 6}{}{Me? I'm Mickey, the polite and considerate treasure hunter from Broken Hills.}
{Speech 6 Answer 8}{}{A treasure hunter?}
{Speech 6 Answer Exit}{}{How nice. All the best.}
{Speech 7}{}{Don't tell me you've never heard of me! Has nobody ever told you the tales of Quick Mickey? Of his amazing gunfights, devastating raids, and the enemy faces he's smashed in?}
{Speech 7 Answer 9}{}{Nope.}
{Speech 8}{}{Don't tell me you've never heard of me! Has nobody ever told you the tales of Quick Mickey? Of his amazing gunfights, devastating raids, and the enemy faces he's smashed in?}
{Speech 8 Answer 10}{}{I'm afraid that pleasure has passed me by.}
{Speech 9}{}{Время:60000 Нет ответа:Завершить диалог}
{Speech 9 Answer Exit}{}{Aaall riiight!}
{Speech 10}{}{Время:60000 Нет ответа:Завершить диалог}
{Speech 10 Answer Exit}{}{I'll wait with bated breath.}
{Speech 11}{}{Время:60000 Нет ответа:Завершить диалог / Close dialog}
{Speech 11 Answer 12}{}{No problem!}
{Speech 12}{}{Время:60000 Нет ответа:Завершить диалог / Close dialog}
{Speech 12 Answer 12}{}{You'll be the first on my list.}
{Speech 13}{}{Hi. I'm Mickey. Hear me out.\n}
{Speech 13 Answer Exit}{}{Get lost, you damn runt. I don't give to beggars.}
{Speech 13 Answer 14}{}{I'm listening, what happened?}
{Speech 14}{}{I'm a treasure hunter, you see. So, some guy showed up around here not long ago…}
{Speech 14 Answer Exit}{}{A hunter, my ass… Have you looked in a mirror? Get lost…}
{Speech 14 Answer 15}{}{Stuffed with treasure, was he?}
{Speech 15}{}{No, listen on.  He wanted to find some locals for a risky job. Hmm. But the folks around here are a hard lot to get moving.}
{Speech 15 Answer 16}{}{So, what then?}
{Speech 15 Answer Exit}{}{Just like it should be in a godforsaken hole. That's it, I've got no time.}
{Speech 16}{}{So I went up to him - like, I'll take it on. But he brushed me off.  And laughed at me too, the bastard. But there's something interesting going on with him, I can smell it. You know what a nose I've got for treasure? Whoa!}
{Speech 16 Answer Exit}{}{Right, you go sniff then, I've gotta go.}
{Speech 16 Answer 17}{}{Let's get to the point already.}
{Speech 17}{}{So here's what I'm offering you - go talk to him. He's got something interesting there, for sure. I guarantee it. And for the tip-off, give me… well, I don't know. Bring me something unusual. Or toss me some money once the deal pans out.\n}
{Speech 17 Answer 18}{}{Hmm. All right, I'll talk to him. Where is he?}
{Speech 18}{}{He's been hanging around the bar lately. Something's wrong with his arm.\n}
{Speech 18 Answer Exit}{}{Okay, got it. I'll go take a look now.}
{Speech 19}{}{So how'd it go with my tip-off? Did the deal pan out?}
{Speech 19 Answer 20}{}{Yeah, you could say that.}
{Speech 20}{}{Whoa, and what was there? Will I get anything out of it?}
{Speech 20 Answer 21}{}{Well, I got a few shots to the head out of it. I can share.}
{Speech 21}{}{Eeeh, no thanks. Sorry.}
